						               													<description>Heavy Metal meets Fantasy. Book of Skulls: Slayers of Eragoth board game is a huge dungeon-crawling adventure where two teams battle to save the continent of Eragoth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For 2-4 players in 2 teams. Teams act as the others&amp;rsquo; opponents, whilst one team controls the heroic Slayers of Eragoth, the opposing team will control the Demons they encounter until it is time to switch to their own Slayers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective whilst controlling the Slayers is to clear the Overworld and defeat the final boss first, whilst controlling the Demons your aim is to defeat the opposing team&amp;rsquo;s Slayers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Replay value and combat is at the heart of Book of Skulls. &amp;#10;During your adventure, you will have access to over 150 unique characters, each with their own movesets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Set the Overworld using 10 interchangeable modular maps (levels) that each represent a unique region of Eragoth. A different adventure awaits with each game as any number of levels can be selected and placed in any order, allowing you to customise the duration of your game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Book of Skulls is fully soundtracked with an original Metal soundtrack which perfectly sets the mood for battling the Demons of Eragoth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
